                            Icon Programs  v2.0
              A collection of icon/tooltype-related programs.
                             ©1997  J. Tierney


The Programs:
@{"InfoReq    " link PRG_IREQ}  Open Workbench's icon information requester.

@{"CloneIcon  " link PRG_CLONE}  Make copies of an icon.
@{"MakeDefIcon" link PRG_MKDEF}  Create icons for iconless files.

@{"FileToTT   " link PRG_FTT}  Copy a text file to an icon's tooltype list.
@{"TTToFile   " link PRG_TTF}  Copy an icon's tooltypes to a text file.


@{"Legalities " link SMEG}  They're PD, and nothing's my fault.
@{"Credits    " link GRACIAS}  Many thanks to...
@{"History    " link PAST}
@{"The Author " link SMEGHEAD}  Hey, that's me!
@endnode


